                                </div>
                                <div class="item4 ">
                                    <ul style="list-style-type:suqre">
                                        <li class="marginBottom">We share your name and contact details with other users when you post cattle for sale on the Platform. This allows them to contact you if they’re interested in making a purchase;</li>
                                        <li>We also share your name and contact details with our delivery partners. This helps them reach out to you when delivering cattle and products.</li>
